{
  "stem": "9963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We thought we're-- we will run deeper to Poland, what the-- the Germans will be stopped, because, you know, the radios always, you know, said how strong Poland is, and Poland will stop them, you know, when they called, and then things like this.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we ran deeper to Poland, but it was not so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Germans came in, they just went through Poland without a fight, practically.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came, already they owe us about 250 to 300 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went there-- day in and day night-- day and night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- as far as [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this is already quite a bit away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans say they got us around, but we couldn't go no place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans was already there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to go back to home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the minute when we can back home, we've seen already what the hell started.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because like the Germans start to taking the Jewish people to work, taking the Orthodox Jewish people, cutting their beards, cutting their payos.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's a beating them, killing them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so soon I came home with my brothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had my older brother, what is now in Paris, France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had-- where he was working, he had the boys and girls afraid, what they-- they said they cannot stay there and work for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they said they-- they will go across the other 1/2 of Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because at that time, the Russian took already 1/2 Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Germans had-- had the other 1/2.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they went to the border, and they were-- went over the border, what was water over there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They swim that through, and-- to be on the Russian sector.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my brother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother what is Paris, France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I stayed at home.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
